To do so, choose **Transpose Tidy to Source** main menu’s **Edit** menu, or use
the shortcut key as indicated.

<%= pne %> will try its best to preserve the location of your insertion point so
that you can continue typing immediately, however certain changes – especially
if there are many of them – will affect this position.

